Mr Maangi, Ruto’s pointman in Gusii, said the meeting was meant to unite leaders allied to the DP.Just last month, Mr Maangi pledged to work with Dr Matiang’i in what he said will help galvanise the unity of Abagusii. Deputy President William Ruto has held talks with leaders from Kisii and Baringo counties in an effort to solidify his support.
The DP met Baringo leaders yesterday and on Thursday, he had held talks with Gusii leaders. In Kisii, the leaders have been reading from different scripts, especially after his decision to shun leading the “No” side of the BBI referendum.



